{"tid":280700,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"色魔係籃球佬","createTime":"2017-06-12T09:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T11:48:48.000Z","uid":3806,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9619f092b6dff80ee4ba1d24543192028837e2","tid":280700,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497243950_9e9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497243950_9e9b.jpg&h=7489b690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屯門寶田邨發生令人髮指的強姦案(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2r8AFq3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2r8AFq3&d=rGbzPBv%2FvAtRghWU3Hqj%2BUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=9f58c5fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2r8AFq3</a>)，涉案男子仍被扣留調查。據知情人士透露，被捕男子6年前亦因在屯門區尾隨獨行女子返家，劫財劫色，他被捕後判囚6年半，早前才刑滿出獄，豈料又涉強姦案被捕。疑犯一名中學同學，對他屢次涉犯風化案感到可惜，有女同學更直言，日後如在街上撞見他，會兜路走。<br />\n<br />\n今次案中的被捕疑犯「阿文」，28歲。據其相熟的同學爆料稱，阿文中學時成績一般，「<span style=\"color: red;\">以前一齊打籃球，都好friend，佢主要打三分</span>。」該同學指出，阿文常向朋友稱喜歡胸部豐滿的女性，但萬料不到，他於2011年會犯下非禮及搶劫罪。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，當時22歲的阿文，涉嫌在屯門區內先後尾隨兩名女子返家，其中一名女事主更被推往後樓梯，被人以刀指頸搶走手機，有人更迫令她口交，女事主復遭在臉上射精及以精液塗臉，阿文事後被捕判監禁6年半。<br />\n<br />\n阿文的舊同學稱，約半年前已在屯門區內多次撞見阿文，估計他剛出獄，「喺輕鐵站都見過幾次，佢主動話約出嚟食嘢，見佢個樣冇變，都係著短衫短褲波鞋look。」阿文的舊同學又說，一班女生談到如阿文今次再判監，日後出獄，「佢哋話撞見都會兜路走，但我就唔會，希望佢得到適當治療，唔好再犯事。」["},{"pid":"7bbad0eacf1128c98f3ccf2cd10e100d75bc0ecf","tid":280700,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"籃波撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265c8c38d5f4ec8b2aa0e09e29abe8f2af782b71","tid":280700,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>籃波撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220e73f60be5bc5b2a80c61c0f97ef2b911a1420","tid":280700,"uid":138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"玩具狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d887b67e24bd62ec3aff3cf28591da0ef505c6a8","tid":280700,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"左圖高咁多咁既"},{"pid":"7c902b8ee1ca6d848313067765fec12989b6a2a7","tid":280700,"uid":8404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:22:22.000Z","msg":"猩猩們麻煩出黎解釋下"},{"pid":"cbb781cf065c4a853db0db39dc161c130a751331","tid":280700,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"學c朗姐"},{"pid":"8bce8c413eb81cb99849358e4e72a02ca0471dce","tid":280700,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"卡勞高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480b02518f5b30baa48642795188ef8816c9e70a","tid":280700,"uid":16281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2578919084820dbb152343622d68ecb8b94805cc","tid":280700,"uid":16281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:36:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a8dbbd4591938212fc3f793b22bab3a425a1ec4","tid":280700,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:36:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果個女仔生到似麻友g<br />\n佢就唔會犯案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n佢會犯毆打罪"},{"pid":"cca92df2c435087bc53b1e8ad64e2b67c67ca858","tid":280700,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ec4239c9070b1ef8211e4f14022c57a96acaaf","tid":280700,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-